Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:18.38,Always EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}But I know what's truly precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:26.84,Always EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}The way, it leads me to be in love,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:38.02,Always EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}No fear, I can find me always in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:12.06,Always EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}I swear to go whatever will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:19.81,Always EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}Thus the grace I would had will always in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:32.41,Always EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}Thus the grace I would had will always in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:37.84,Always CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}倘若前路  已成定数
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:44.80,Always CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}尽我此生  艰行难住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:53.23,Always CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}履之能及  不问何处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:21:02.57,Always CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}心有所冀  毕生求溯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:11.04,Always CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}命若风烛  亡逝何怵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:18.38,Always CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}蒹葭倚玉  千金敝帚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:26.84,Always CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}两情相依  缘起此途
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:38.02,Always CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}寸心得守  死生何顾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:12.06,Always CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}履之所及  不问何处
